# Force LF line endings on checkout across all platforms. The repo is authored
# on macOS/Linux (LF), so this only changes what Windows checks out — it keeps
# the generated-docs drift tests (e.g. test/docs-sync.test.ts) byte-identical to
# their LF originals on the Windows CI runner.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets git must never touch.
*.png binary
